？"},{"pid":"692c03713f4068d961845199fbc34e5512a2e315","tid":686303,"uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實當年港府搞免費教育係被逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>其實世界所有國家搞免費教育都係被逼。<br />\n冇公共教育，邊到黎有基礎知識嘅工人？</blockquote>當年港府係因為童工問題嚴重所以先搞9年免費教育<br />\n其他野係side effect<br />\n(好似係)</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係提前兩年實施　點解講到走o左樣？<br />\n<br />\n仲有　全名係九年免費強迫教育<br />\n<br />\n除o左童工　仲有街童問題　的晒班細路哥返學　個問題咪解決o左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有　之前已經有6年免費強迫教育<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n麥理浩有工黨背景　佢政策有工黨影子都好正常啫<br />\n咁o岩當時香港同英國o係工業有競爭<br />\n英國商人咪支持　認為香港加福利加政府開支可以降低香港工業競爭力<br />\n咁英國國會咪支持佢做法<br />\n<br />\n除工黨背景　麥理浩仲係蘇格蘭人　對身份認同議題亦都冇可能冇認識"},{"pid":"ff551a5088abfe7942789a5423af1f6ffbff39ae","tid":686303,"uid":92301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"176bce0475e4ab2b4ca955e99a5436815fa8b242","tid":686303,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10:12:23.000Z","msg":"作者乜水？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T11:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/30629008_223556921531002_3772030472927594920_n.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;_nc_eui2=AeFnF-dhTR2_O3U5zxBMlmiQmQ1T2GCdWuEX0XdGw-vtUQlYAKE8J_etRnnubCGD7SJWajtJ-cdmZiZYuRoN2zEbVX02l2N7h5wLIGfKQsYH9g&amp;oh=95a41f3c831c52bc80c747cc3d4bfb62&amp;oe=5B7EEFDD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F30629008_223556921531002_3772030472927594920_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26_nc_eui2%3DAeFnF-dhTR2_O3U5zxBMlmiQmQ1T2GCdWuEX0XdGw-vtUQlYAKE8J_etRnnubCGD7SJWajtJ-cdmZiZYuRoN2zEbVX02l2N7h5wLIGfKQsYH9g%26oh%3D95a41f3c831c52bc80c747cc3d4bfb62%26oe%3D5B7EEFDD&h=c268b811&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"15c7422649bd456edc294c821314cceb88928843","tid":686303,"uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ba2a68a49b7169741879b70fcc9