講歷史。講英國佬既較實在，例如bno由來，英國為香港爭取保障等，可能因為有個xxx計劃既組織提供英國檔案參考<br />\n<br />\n但講中共既就相當簡略<br />\n<br />\n用類同作品比較，eg憂鬱的家邦，香港獨x論，或新出嗰本'積極不干預'，內容上差距係非常非常大。買既唯一理由係支持本土作者<br />\n<br />\n因此，不得不評估吓作者既背景<br />\n<br />\n有兩點頗在意：<br />\n1. 本書話喺潘x凱（炎黃解毒作者）協助下出版<br />\n個人對此人背景及政治立場非常懷疑<br />\n<br />\n2. 有一段大概係咁：<br />\n'<span style=\"color: red;\">白話（粵文）</span>與英語都係香港主要語言⋯⋯'<br />\n<br />\n然後後面繼續用白話稱呼廣東話<br />\n<br />\n咁樣講，一來柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，二來只有大陸人先會講廣東話係白話<br />\n<br />\n查實有冇人知道多啲作者同所屬組織背景？"},{"pid":"90afd634d1aaf425ea89978c897e7a5dd376c7f8","tid":686303,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"多謝書評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9acc3eab717b1d272367eb8acb4146a257d52f2","tid":686303,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06b6d4875689ea444758aab8bbfd19323872cdfe","tid":686303,"uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c261d7b371461a6d8a74dd4820a2e9e3f8e9df02","tid":686303,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"176bce0475e4ab2b4ca955e99a5436815fa8b242","tid":686303,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10:12:23.000Z","msg":"作者乜水？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T10:30:35.000Z","msg":"x2"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T14:04:16.000Z","msg":"The Blue Party 創辦人<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/43/119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Fprog%2F43%2F119&d=JnLVKeEM%2FheA9YYMrJKQbzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=64f6ee88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/prog/43/119</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T16:47:40.000Z","msg":"熱狗？"},{"pid":"e6b3937c67f7ff4cf755d7ae18b917990137bbd6","tid":686303,"uid":147314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a5afe67323dc2326cd02a68bf18ef50b85685775","tid":686303,"uid":48083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"cit